WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:35.719 --> 00:01:36.840
Yanyun

00:01:37.359 --> 00:01:39.200
dares to oppose me

00:01:41.760 --> 00:01:42.840
only because

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:45.920
His Majesty backs him.

00:01:47.319 --> 00:01:49.599
The Li family has finally produced

00:01:49.599 --> 00:01:51.719
a half-decent emperor,

00:01:53.719 --> 00:01:54.560
though

00:01:55.239 --> 00:01:56.439
a bit too impatient.

00:01:56.879 --> 00:01:58.040
He's eager to handle state affairs himself.

00:01:58.480 --> 00:01:59.719
But the court

00:01:59.719 --> 00:02:02.280
is already a mess.

00:02:02.959 --> 00:02:04.079
How could

00:02:04.840 --> 00:02:06.319
a boy like him

00:02:06.319 --> 00:02:07.319
fix it?

00:02:07.560 --> 00:02:08.159
Your Excellency,

00:02:08.840 --> 00:02:10.159
as far as I'm concerned,

00:02:10.680 --> 00:02:11.719
His Majesty is young

00:02:12.199 --> 00:02:13.520
and doesn't understand

00:02:13.719 --> 00:02:14.639
your good intentions.

00:02:15.120 --> 00:02:16.439
You spent years

00:02:17.039 --> 00:02:18.080
cultivating Yanyun

00:02:18.080 --> 00:02:19.599
and even entrusted

00:02:20.199 --> 00:02:22.400
His Majesty to his care.

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:23.800
Yet

00:02:24.439 --> 00:02:25.479
in the end,

00:02:26.919 --> 00:02:28.599
he betrayed you

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:31.439
and led His Majesty astray.

00:02:34.759 --> 00:02:36.919
I made him what he is.

00:02:37.840 --> 00:02:39.280
I can...

00:02:50.039 --> 00:02:50.719
Yu, you're here?
Go

00:02:51.800 --> 00:02:52.879
make a pot of

00:02:52.879 --> 00:02:53.800
the finest tea.

00:02:54.759 --> 00:02:55.120
Yes.

00:02:55.599 --> 00:02:57.479
Thanks.

00:02:58.879 --> 00:03:00.560
I heard something interesting

00:03:01.240 --> 00:03:01.840
and came to

00:03:02.080 --> 00:03:03.439
report it to you.

00:03:05.479 --> 00:03:06.199
What is it?

00:03:06.639 --> 00:03:07.840
The candidate list

00:03:07.840 --> 00:03:10.840
for Daily Lecturer posts at Hanlin Academy.

00:03:11.639 --> 00:03:13.080
Let me see.

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:14.080
What's wrong?

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:15.599
Nothing.

00:03:16.039 --> 00:03:16.919
Except

00:03:17.639 --> 00:03:18.960
one name is missing.

00:03:21.159 --> 00:03:21.960
Who?

00:03:22.599 --> 00:03:23.960
Chen Xuanqing.

00:03:27.479 --> 00:03:28.319
He really isn't.

00:03:29.080 --> 00:03:30.360
I've asked around.

00:03:30.639 --> 00:03:31.560
Guess what I found?

00:03:33.039 --> 00:03:33.800
He's being transferred.

00:03:35.759 --> 00:03:36.400
Really?

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:38.159
To Anqing Prefecture.

00:03:38.159 --> 00:03:40.319
Yanyun arranged it himself.

00:03:41.319 --> 00:03:42.120
Well,

00:03:42.439 --> 00:03:43.520
everyone knows

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:46.159
Chen Xuanqing is the nephew

00:03:46.159 --> 00:03:47.800
Yanyun took in.

00:03:48.759 --> 00:03:50.879
The boy is talented,

00:03:51.199 --> 00:03:51.879
so

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:53.919
Yanyun has had high hopes for him.

00:03:54.560 --> 00:03:56.000
Coming third in the imperial exams,

00:03:56.599 --> 00:03:58.319
entering the Hanlin Academy,

00:03:58.800 --> 00:03:59.759
and later

00:03:59.879 --> 00:04:01.479
serving as an envoy to the northern steppe.

00:04:02.319 --> 00:04:03.599
Quite a distinguished record.

00:04:04.759 --> 00:04:06.639
Yanyun had paved the way for him

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:08.599
and was

00:04:08.960 --> 00:04:10.479
clearly grooming him

00:04:10.479 --> 00:04:11.479
as his successor.

00:04:11.479 --> 00:04:12.599
Now Xuanqing's

00:04:13.439 --> 00:04:14.840
sidelined to Anqing.

00:04:15.919 --> 00:04:16.720
I'd say

00:04:17.079 --> 00:04:18.639
there's been a falling-out between them,

00:04:19.079 --> 00:04:20.319
and not

00:04:21.399 --> 00:04:22.680
a small one.

00:04:29.759 --> 00:04:30.959
That's interesting.

00:04:34.360 --> 00:04:35.240
As you asked, I took men

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:36.600
to the northern border to investigate

00:04:36.920 --> 00:04:37.560
and

00:04:37.839 --> 00:04:39.120
did find traces

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:40.319
of the Chunyuan remnants.

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:42.839
How many?

00:04:44.199 --> 00:04:45.560
At first, we only found

00:04:45.839 --> 00:04:46.879
a dozen or so.

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:48.920
But as I followed the trail,

00:04:49.160 --> 00:04:49.959
I found more of them.

00:04:50.360 --> 00:04:51.800
Those hand signs you told me about

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:52.720
really helped.

00:04:53.160 --> 00:04:54.120
Without that lead,

00:04:54.319 --> 00:04:55.279
I never would have found them.

00:04:55.839 --> 00:04:57.360
What do they do for a living?

00:04:58.079 --> 00:04:59.639
The poor ones take odd jobs,

00:04:59.839 --> 00:05:00.839
while the rich ones run businesses.

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:02.560
They're in all walks of life.

00:05:03.920 --> 00:05:05.319
Got any leads on their leader?

00:05:07.319 --> 00:05:07.920
Mr. Chen.

00:05:09.319 --> 00:05:10.600
No need for formalities.

00:05:10.879 --> 00:05:11.399
Have a seat.

00:05:14.279 --> 00:05:15.000
Please go on.

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:17.399
I looked into their leader as well.

00:05:18.600 --> 00:05:19.800
The Chunyuan Sect Master

00:05:20.560 --> 00:05:21.439
is very mysterious.

00:05:21.959 --> 00:05:23.279
No one knows what he looks like.

00:05:23.879 --> 00:05:24.439
However,

00:05:24.759 --> 00:05:25.639
I did uncover
an important clue.

00:05:27.240 --> 00:05:28.800
Back when Prince Chengqing's rebellion failed,

00:05:29.480 --> 00:05:30.600
these Chunyuan sect members

00:05:30.839 --> 00:05:31.839
managed to flee from the capital

00:05:32.120 --> 00:05:33.040
to the northern steppe

00:05:33.399 --> 00:05:35.160
because someone was secretly funding them.

00:05:37.160 --> 00:05:37.800
Who?

00:05:38.319 --> 00:05:39.199
Someone known

00:05:40.079 --> 00:05:41.000
as Lady Weirui.

00:05:43.279 --> 00:05:44.399
Lady Weirui?

00:05:45.079 --> 00:05:45.839
Even I

00:05:45.839 --> 00:05:46.959
have never heard of such a person.

00:05:48.439 --> 00:05:49.040
Miss.

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:52.160
Miss,

00:05:52.399 --> 00:05:53.639
this is a letter from Ms. Xue.

00:06:01.360 --> 00:06:02.480
Qinglan says

00:06:02.680 --> 00:06:03.959
she'd like to meet us.

00:06:08.639 --> 00:06:09.560
Sorry to disturb you so late.

00:06:09.560 --> 00:06:10.600
I'll get straight to the point.

00:06:11.079 --> 00:06:12.279
What have you

00:06:12.279 --> 00:06:13.560
found out about the Chunyuan Sect?

00:06:17.079 --> 00:06:18.079
Haven't you been

00:06:18.079 --> 00:06:20.000
investigating with Xian?

00:06:20.639 --> 00:06:21.639
Why not ask him?

00:06:21.920 --> 00:06:22.639
I did,

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:23.720
but he wouldn't tell me.

00:06:24.319 --> 00:06:25.439
I have my own reasons

00:06:25.439 --> 00:06:26.600
for looking into the Chunyuan Sect.

00:06:27.160 --> 00:06:27.720
Don't worry.

00:06:28.279 --> 00:06:29.279
I won't reveal anything.

00:06:29.480 --> 00:06:30.680
Nor will I act against you.

00:06:31.319 --> 00:06:32.160
In fact,

00:06:32.639 --> 00:06:33.560
we're after the same
thing.

00:06:35.639 --> 00:06:36.720
If I'm not mistaken,

00:06:37.160 --> 00:06:38.360
you want to track down

00:06:38.360 --> 00:06:39.519
the Chunyuan Sect

00:06:40.120 --> 00:06:41.000
because

00:06:41.560 --> 00:06:42.480
of your late mother.

00:06:44.879 --> 00:06:45.839
I've heard that

00:06:46.600 --> 00:06:48.240
over a decade ago, she was

00:06:48.600 --> 00:06:50.279
killed by Chunyuan Sect members.

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:53.120
What are you doing?

00:06:53.560 --> 00:06:54.639
That was supposed to be a secret.

00:06:55.600 --> 00:06:56.759
How do you know this?

00:06:56.759 --> 00:06:57.959
As a Grand Secretary,

00:06:58.759 --> 00:06:59.519
of course I know

00:07:00.680 --> 00:07:02.240
more than most people.

00:07:02.879 --> 00:07:03.680
Otherwise,

00:07:04.079 --> 00:07:05.319
how could I

00:07:05.800 --> 00:07:06.519
let you stay

00:07:06.519 --> 00:07:07.839
by Ye Xian's side?

00:07:09.639 --> 00:07:10.319
Qinglan.

00:07:14.560 --> 00:07:15.720
So I'm right about you.

00:07:16.839 --> 00:07:18.040
You've been hiding your hand.

00:07:18.600 --> 00:07:19.120
Right.

00:07:19.759 --> 00:07:20.879
I came to you

00:07:21.079 --> 00:07:22.319
because of my mom.

00:07:23.399 --> 00:07:24.319
Back then, the Chunyuan Sect

00:07:24.319 --> 00:07:25.519
aided Prince Chengqing's rebellion

00:07:26.639 --> 00:07:28.160
and had enormous influence in the capital.

00:07:28.720 --> 00:07:30.519
Many officials and their families

00:07:30.519 --> 00:07:31.439
were assassinated.

00:07:32.560 --> 00:07:34.639
My mom was one of the victims.

00:07:35.639 --> 00:07:36.560
She drank

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:37.720
poisoned tea

00:07:39.040 --> 00:07:39.839
and passed away.

00:07:40.319 --> 00:07:41.959
Have you found any leads?

00:07:42.480 --> 00:07:43.560
If I had,

00:07:43.560 --> 00:07:44.680
would I be here asking you?

00:07:45.560 --> 00:07:46.399
But I know

00:07:46.959 --> 00:07:48.480
the one who poisoned her

00:07:48.759 --> 00:07:50.120
must have been someone close to her.

00:07:52.160 --> 00:07:53.959
Sounds like you already

00:07:54.319 --> 00:07:56.000
have someone in mind.

00:07:56.399 --> 00:07:57.040
You must know

00:07:57.040 --> 00:07:58.199
more than I do.

00:07:59.560 --> 00:08:00.079
Tell me.

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:02.079
Who is truly behind

00:08:02.279 --> 00:08:03.160
the Chunyuan Sect?

00:08:03.439 --> 00:08:04.480
I only have suspicions.

00:08:04.600 --> 00:08:05.519
No solid evidence yet.

00:08:06.480 --> 00:08:07.879
On the day Wang Xuanfan

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:10.120
and his wife died,

00:08:10.519 --> 00:08:11.360
Jinzhao, Xian,

00:08:11.879 --> 00:08:12.519
and I

00:08:12.519 --> 00:08:13.720
saw the bodies.

00:08:16.279 --> 00:08:17.439
So you suspect

00:08:17.439 --> 00:08:19.040
the mastermind is

00:08:20.839 --> 00:08:21.720
my uncle?

00:08:22.319 --> 00:08:23.079
As I said,

00:08:24.279 --> 00:08:25.879
there's no proof yet.

00:08:28.360 --> 00:08:28.839
Alright.

00:08:29.920 --> 00:08:30.680
I get it.

00:08:32.159 --> 00:08:33.519
Thank you for telling me these.

00:08:33.840 --> 00:08:35.639
I owe you a favor.

00:08:36.080 --> 00:08:37.279
No need for that.

00:08:38.600 --> 00:08:39.360
What do you mean?

00:08:40.360 --> 00:08:41.720
You are my master's niece

00:08:42.399 --> 00:08:43.919
and a daughter of the Xue family.

00:08:44.639 --> 00:08:45.200
But

00:08:45.639 --> 00:08:47.159
above all, you're a subject of Great Yan.

00:08:47.840 --> 00:08:49.320
Ms. Xue, I only hope that

00:08:49.879 --> 00:08:50.440
when

00:08:50.440 --> 00:08:51.919
hard choices come,

00:08:53.159 --> 00:08:54.600
you can do the right thing.

00:09:12.159 --> 00:09:13.200
The clown actor

00:09:13.759 --> 00:09:15.080
looks kinda familiar.

00:09:15.799 --> 00:09:17.159
I feel like I've seen him somewhere.

00:09:17.440 --> 00:09:19.080
You don't know?

00:09:19.399 --> 00:09:21.320
That's Chen Yanyun's nephew,

00:09:21.519 --> 00:09:22.759
Chen Xuanqing.

00:11:00.440 --> 00:11:01.320
Your Excellency.

00:11:03.240 --> 00:11:04.159
I caught a bit of

00:11:04.159 --> 00:11:05.279
your performance just now.

00:11:05.720 --> 00:11:06.559
Not bad at all.

00:11:08.320 --> 00:11:09.480
The stage makeup suits you too.

00:11:10.159 --> 00:11:11.279
You performed

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:12.879
this well after just one lesson.

00:11:13.279 --> 00:11:13.759
Very clever.

00:11:14.440 --> 00:11:15.240
I'm flattered.

00:11:17.320 --> 00:11:18.399
If you don't want to leave the capital,

00:11:18.399 --> 00:11:20.399
you should ask your uncle for help.

00:11:20.399 --> 00:11:21.240
Why

00:11:21.440 --> 00:11:22.799
did you come to me?

00:11:24.279 --> 00:11:25.679
I did go to him,

00:11:26.480 --> 00:11:27.600
but he refused.

00:11:27.759 --> 00:11:28.360
Why?

00:11:31.919 --> 00:11:32.559
Probably

00:11:34.480 --> 00:11:36.279
because I'm eager to stand out

00:11:36.559 --> 00:11:37.759
and end up displeasing my uncle.

00:11:38.759 --> 00:11:39.320
Besides,

00:11:39.799 --> 00:11:41.000
I'm not of the Chen bloodline.

00:11:41.240 --> 00:11:42.360
I'm adopted.

00:11:45.399 --> 00:11:46.759
You wanna stay in the capital?

00:11:47.279 --> 00:11:47.679
Yes.

00:11:49.200 --> 00:11:50.000
Are you aware

00:11:50.000 --> 00:11:51.039
that your uncle

00:11:51.240 --> 00:11:52.519
used to be my student,

00:11:52.720 --> 00:11:54.559
but we're now

00:11:55.200 --> 00:11:56.600
bitter enemies?

00:11:58.960 --> 00:11:59.759
I am.

00:12:00.480 --> 00:12:01.120
That is

00:12:01.120 --> 00:12:02.519
precisely why I came.

00:12:08.480 --> 00:12:09.519
I may not be gifted,

00:12:09.720 --> 00:12:10.840
but my loyalty is absolute.

00:12:11.799 --> 00:12:13.559
I'm willing to serve you.

00:12:37.679 --> 00:12:38.320
Good.

00:12:45.360 --> 00:12:46.360
Ms. Yu,

00:12:46.759 --> 00:12:48.559
you're already drunk.

00:12:51.080 --> 00:12:52.799
What do I do?

00:12:55.600 --> 00:12:56.000
Miss.
How is she?

00:12:56.639 --> 00:12:57.679
She's on her second pot.

00:12:58.120 --> 00:12:59.120
I couldn't stop her.

00:12:59.440 --> 00:13:00.399
The moment I tried,

00:13:00.519 --> 00:13:01.519
she started crying.

00:13:07.080 --> 00:13:07.960
Stop drinking.

00:13:14.600 --> 00:13:16.519
Why torture yourself like this?

00:13:17.240 --> 00:13:18.080
You know

00:13:18.080 --> 00:13:19.519
Chen Xuanqing isn't the right man.

00:13:19.679 --> 00:13:20.559
I only told you not to marry him

00:13:20.559 --> 00:13:21.639
for your own good.

00:13:29.039 --> 00:13:30.399
I said stop.

00:13:31.360 --> 00:13:32.440
Give it to me.

00:13:32.919 --> 00:13:34.200
Give it back.

00:13:35.759 --> 00:13:36.320
Ziling,

00:13:36.919 --> 00:13:37.480
have Zhidi

00:13:37.639 --> 00:13:38.759
bring the carriage to the back door.

00:13:39.000 --> 00:13:39.919
Yes.

00:13:45.200 --> 00:13:46.279
I'm taking you home.

00:13:47.120 --> 00:13:48.480
I'm not going back.

00:13:48.679 --> 00:13:49.200
Come on.

00:13:49.320 --> 00:13:50.399
I'm not going!

00:13:50.399 --> 00:13:50.960
Move.

00:13:54.120 --> 00:13:55.519
- I don't wanna go back.
- Watch your step.

00:13:56.399 --> 00:13:57.919
- I won't go.
- Get in.

00:13:57.919 --> 00:13:58.840
Let go of me.

00:13:59.080 --> 00:13:59.679
No.

00:14:02.519 --> 00:14:03.879
Xuanqing?

00:14:07.120 --> 00:14:08.399
- Xuanqing?
- Where are you going?

00:14:09.600 --> 00:14:10.519
Xuanqing.

00:14:13.320 --> 00:14:14.120
Xuanqing,

00:14:14.120 --> 00:14:15.200
it's me, Wanxue.

00:14:15.960 --> 00:14:17.000
Xuanqing.

00:14:22.480 --> 00:14:23.279
Xuanqing?

00:14:26.240 --> 00:14:27.120
Xuanqing!

00:14:27.120 --> 00:14:28.159
Xuanqing, don't go.

00:14:28.519 --> 00:14:29.320
Xuanqing!

00:14:31.120 --> 00:14:31.600
Xuanqing?

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:33.120
Xuanqing? Xuanqing?

00:14:33.919 --> 00:14:34.960
Xuanqing, wait.

00:14:35.519 --> 00:14:37.639
Xuanqing, Xuanqing!

00:14:37.919 --> 00:14:39.360
Xuanqing!

00:14:39.759 --> 00:14:40.679
Stop yelling.

00:14:40.879 --> 00:14:41.919
He doesn't wanna see you.

00:14:42.159 --> 00:14:42.559
That's good.

00:14:42.759 --> 00:14:43.879
We don't want to see him either.

00:14:44.399 --> 00:14:45.360
Help me get her back.

00:14:45.759 --> 00:14:47.039
Xuanqing!

00:14:47.039 --> 00:14:47.519
Come on.

00:14:47.720 --> 00:14:49.559
- Xuanqing!
- Stop looking back.

00:14:49.559 --> 00:14:50.320
- Wanxue.
- Careful.

00:14:52.000 --> 00:14:53.000
Please don't go.

00:15:07.279 --> 00:15:08.960
That will be all for today's morning court.

00:15:12.200 --> 00:15:14.600
Is Your Majesty heading to the Wenhua Hall?

00:15:15.159 --> 00:15:15.639
Indeed.

00:15:16.120 --> 00:15:17.080
Today,

00:15:17.320 --> 00:15:19.639
the lecturers will test me on my studies.

00:15:20.480 --> 00:15:22.480
I'm rather nervous about it.

00:15:23.679 --> 00:15:25.720
I haven't checked on

00:15:25.720 --> 00:15:27.000
Your Majesty's studies lately.

00:15:27.360 --> 00:15:30.159
Why not summon the lecturers

00:15:30.320 --> 00:15:32.080
here instead,

00:15:32.399 --> 00:15:35.360
so we can all observe?

00:15:36.440 --> 00:15:38.679
Mr. Fu, you wanna

00:15:38.960 --> 00:15:40.120
test the lecturers

00:15:40.360 --> 00:15:41.559
on my behalf first?

00:15:42.159 --> 00:15:42.799
Zhang Fang,

00:15:43.720 --> 00:15:45.879
summon the lecturers here.

00:15:46.240 --> 00:15:47.639
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:15:51.360 --> 00:15:54.120
The lecturers have arrived!

00:16:12.039 --> 00:16:12.720
We, Chen Xuanqing,
Chu Junliang, and Li Rufei,

00:16:13.679 --> 00:16:14.639
humbly pay our respects.

00:16:14.879 --> 00:16:16.960
Long live Your Majesty.

00:16:17.080 --> 00:16:17.639
Please rise.

00:16:18.000 --> 00:16:19.159
Thanks, Your Majesty.

00:16:33.200 --> 00:16:33.919
Xuanqing,

00:16:34.440 --> 00:16:35.559
why are you here?

00:16:37.559 --> 00:16:38.320
Your Majesty,

00:16:38.759 --> 00:16:39.720
Lecturer Liu's ill and has taken leave.

00:16:40.000 --> 00:16:41.039
Chancellor Wu has asked me

00:16:41.360 --> 00:16:41.919
to take his place.

00:16:43.679 --> 00:16:44.519
Great.

00:16:45.360 --> 00:16:47.000
The last time I saw you was

00:16:47.320 --> 00:16:49.320
when you returned from the northern steppe.

00:16:49.879 --> 00:16:51.720
Half a year has passed,

00:16:52.639 --> 00:16:54.120
and you look even more impressive.

00:16:54.759 --> 00:16:55.840
Let us begin

00:16:56.159 --> 00:16:57.200
with you today.

00:16:57.759 --> 00:16:59.159
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:17:00.679 --> 00:17:01.600
I...

00:17:11.440 --> 00:17:12.319
[Impeach]

00:17:12.920 --> 00:17:13.720
my uncle?

00:17:14.359 --> 00:17:14.839
I...

00:17:15.519 --> 00:17:16.359
On what grounds?

00:17:17.279 --> 00:17:18.480
For corrupt morals,

00:17:18.880 --> 00:17:20.039
scandalous conduct,

00:17:20.240 --> 00:17:21.319
stealing your wife,

00:17:21.559 --> 00:17:23.440
and defying moral decency.

00:17:23.720 --> 00:17:24.200
This...

00:17:27.200 --> 00:17:27.720
How...

00:17:28.319 --> 00:17:29.640
Where did you hear that?

00:17:30.119 --> 00:17:31.319
There's no such thing.

00:17:40.440 --> 00:17:41.079
Yunting?

00:17:41.960 --> 00:17:42.799
Why are you here?

00:17:46.160 --> 00:17:47.519
Haven't you gone back already?

00:17:47.759 --> 00:17:48.640
What are you doing here?

00:17:49.319 --> 00:17:50.559
I didn't go back.

00:17:53.200 --> 00:17:53.839
I was...

00:18:02.279 --> 00:18:02.799
Sir,

00:18:03.559 --> 00:18:04.680
I'm sorry.

00:18:05.079 --> 00:18:06.799
I'm so sorry.

00:18:08.680 --> 00:18:09.720
They forced me

00:18:10.799 --> 00:18:12.200
to tell them the truth.

00:18:13.119 --> 00:18:15.000
I was terrified.

00:18:19.559 --> 00:18:20.440
What did you say?

00:18:21.039 --> 00:18:23.279
I told them about Nanny Wang.

00:18:25.000 --> 00:18:25.559
And...

00:18:26.160 --> 00:18:27.720
And about you and Mrs. Chen.

00:18:30.519 --> 00:18:32.440
Please forgive me.

00:18:33.119 --> 00:18:35.240
Who would have thought a top scholar

00:18:35.759 --> 00:18:37.000
like you

00:18:37.079 --> 00:18:39.319
would have the nerve to commit murder?

00:18:40.279 --> 00:18:42.640
Seems I misjudged you.

00:18:44.920 --> 00:18:46.119
What a pity.

00:18:49.880 --> 00:18:52.519
I've known Yanyun for over ten years

00:18:53.079 --> 00:18:54.440
and never once saw him

00:18:54.440 --> 00:18:56.039
fall for a woman.

00:18:58.000 --> 00:18:59.079
How surprising.

00:18:59.880 --> 00:19:00.759
They say

00:19:01.039 --> 00:19:02.160
another man's wife is more tempting,

00:19:02.319 --> 00:19:04.079
especially his nephew's.

00:19:16.519 --> 00:19:17.519
Xuanqing,

00:19:20.000 --> 00:19:21.680
His Majesty is talking to you.

00:19:22.160 --> 00:19:22.839
Right.

00:19:23.160 --> 00:19:25.960
What insight do you have for me today?

00:19:32.000 --> 00:19:32.960
Your Majesty,

00:19:33.200 --> 00:19:34.559
before today's lecture,

00:19:35.000 --> 00:19:36.400
I want to impeach someone.

00:19:37.000 --> 00:19:37.400
Oh?

00:19:37.640 --> 00:19:38.599
Who?

00:19:39.279 --> 00:19:40.680
My uncle,

00:19:41.359 --> 00:19:42.319
Grand Secretary

00:19:42.839 --> 00:19:44.319
of the Jianji Hall,

00:19:47.799 --> 00:19:48.920
Chen Yanyun.

00:20:05.440 --> 00:20:07.799
Remember to check the wine lists every day.

00:20:08.519 --> 00:20:09.000
By the way,

00:20:09.400 --> 00:20:10.759
as for wine bought

00:20:10.839 --> 00:20:11.720
by regular customers,

00:20:11.720 --> 00:20:12.920
mark the payment dates in red.

00:20:14.200 --> 00:20:14.680
Okay.

00:20:15.160 --> 00:20:15.799
I got it.

00:20:16.359 --> 00:20:16.839
Hyah!

00:20:23.480 --> 00:20:24.079
Jinzhao?

00:20:26.559 --> 00:20:27.079
Ma'am.

00:20:28.079 --> 00:20:29.079
Mr. Jiang, you...

00:20:29.440 --> 00:20:30.480
Bad news.

00:20:33.839 --> 00:20:35.119
In the 34th year of Jingning era,

00:20:35.319 --> 00:20:36.920
I met Gu Jinzhao at her coming-of-age

00:20:36.920 --> 00:20:37.799
ceremony.

00:20:38.200 --> 00:20:39.359
She fell into the water by accident,

00:20:39.720 --> 00:20:40.279
and I

00:20:40.599 --> 00:20:41.559
saved her life.

00:20:42.279 --> 00:20:43.880
From that, feelings grew between us.

00:20:45.039 --> 00:20:46.079
Yet the Ji family,

00:20:46.279 --> 00:20:47.720
to attach themselves to Chen Yanyun,

00:20:48.240 --> 00:20:49.119
sent her to the capital

00:20:49.119 --> 00:20:51.039
and offered her to him.

00:20:51.880 --> 00:20:52.960
When Chen Yanyun

00:20:53.319 --> 00:20:54.640
learned of our relationship,

00:20:55.319 --> 00:20:57.559
he threatened me with failing imperial exams

00:20:58.640 --> 00:21:00.039
and forced me into

00:21:00.519 --> 00:21:01.839
an engagement with Ms. Yu.

00:21:02.559 --> 00:21:03.640
And while I was away as envoy

00:21:04.400 --> 00:21:05.440
to the northern steppe,

00:21:05.839 --> 00:21:07.359
he forced Jinzhao to marry him.

00:21:07.720 --> 00:21:08.480
Lies!

00:21:08.599 --> 00:21:09.759
Minister Chen isn't that kind of man.

00:21:10.759 --> 00:21:11.480
I have a letter

00:21:11.480 --> 00:21:12.839
from Jinzhao as proof.

00:21:14.200 --> 00:21:15.000
She

00:21:15.240 --> 00:21:17.039
wrote it herself.

00:21:17.400 --> 00:21:18.160
Later, when I

00:21:18.839 --> 00:21:20.279
was forced into the engagement,

00:21:20.599 --> 00:21:21.519
I returned most of her letters

00:21:22.480 --> 00:21:23.440
and kept only one

00:21:23.799 --> 00:21:24.680
to remember her by.

00:21:27.039 --> 00:21:28.240
But this one letter

00:21:28.440 --> 00:21:29.400
is enough to prove

00:21:29.640 --> 00:21:30.440
that she and I

00:21:30.680 --> 00:21:32.079
had pledged ourselves to each other first,

00:21:33.920 --> 00:21:34.920
while Chen Yanyun

00:21:35.400 --> 00:21:36.480
took her by force afterward.

00:21:41.440 --> 00:21:42.680
If I've lied about any of this,

00:21:42.920 --> 00:21:43.480
may I

00:21:43.839 --> 00:21:45.400
die a terrible death.

00:21:46.960 --> 00:21:47.480
You!

00:21:49.359 --> 00:21:50.640
You're called here for the lecture.

00:21:51.119 --> 00:21:51.759
Why

00:21:52.119 --> 00:21:53.519
bring up private matters?

00:21:54.000 --> 00:21:54.599
You...
Your Majesty,

00:21:56.319 --> 00:21:58.160
can I say a few words?

00:21:58.519 --> 00:21:59.519
Go on.

00:22:00.400 --> 00:22:01.599
I recall

00:22:02.480 --> 00:22:03.279
when

00:22:03.559 --> 00:22:05.480
Yanyun married Gu Jinzhao,

00:22:06.519 --> 00:22:07.680
he and Ye Xian

00:22:08.440 --> 00:22:09.960
had a serious clash.

00:22:10.519 --> 00:22:12.240
Ye Xian attempted to kill him

00:22:12.559 --> 00:22:13.319
in the street,

00:22:13.359 --> 00:22:14.720
and they had a fight.

00:22:15.480 --> 00:22:16.319
At the time,

00:22:16.759 --> 00:22:18.559
I told him that self-cultivation,

00:22:19.400 --> 00:22:21.440
household order, and governance

00:22:21.519 --> 00:22:22.480
all matter equally.

00:22:23.160 --> 00:22:23.880
But now

00:22:24.160 --> 00:22:25.759
he and his nephew are fighting

00:22:26.200 --> 00:22:27.759
over the same woman.

00:22:28.559 --> 00:22:29.319
I

00:22:30.039 --> 00:22:32.119
truly cannot make sense of it.

00:22:32.640 --> 00:22:33.720
Xuanqing

00:22:34.000 --> 00:22:35.440
was raised and taught

00:22:35.440 --> 00:22:38.319
by Yanyun himself

00:22:39.559 --> 00:22:42.079
and selected by the late Emperor.

00:22:42.319 --> 00:22:42.799
For him

00:22:43.079 --> 00:22:44.480
to cast aside his dignity

00:22:44.839 --> 00:22:45.920
and future

00:22:46.279 --> 00:22:47.720
and to accuse Yanyun in court,

00:22:48.160 --> 00:22:49.319
he must

00:22:49.839 --> 00:22:51.400
have been driven

00:22:51.960 --> 00:22:53.720
to the brink.

00:22:54.400 --> 00:22:56.799
Yanyun can't keep his household in order,

00:22:57.200 --> 00:22:58.279
and his conduct is disgraceful.

00:22:58.720 --> 00:23:00.160
He's unfit to serve the court.

00:23:00.799 --> 00:23:01.480
I'm

00:23:02.000 --> 00:23:03.960
his master.

00:23:04.960 --> 00:23:07.039
I'm at fault too.

00:23:09.359 --> 00:23:10.640
Please punish me

00:23:11.480 --> 00:23:12.319
as well.

00:23:21.559 --> 00:23:23.599
Chen Yanyun is disgraceful

00:23:23.599 --> 00:23:24.920
and unfit to serve.

00:23:25.160 --> 00:23:25.799
Please

00:23:25.920 --> 00:23:27.200
punish him!

00:23:27.319 --> 00:23:29.599
Your Majesty, punish him!

00:23:29.880 --> 00:23:30.319
This...

00:23:30.839 --> 00:23:32.039
Your Excellency,

00:23:32.559 --> 00:23:34.279
you're pinning the charges

00:23:34.680 --> 00:23:35.319
on me

00:23:36.319 --> 00:23:37.359
in case

00:23:37.599 --> 00:23:39.039
I won't confess.

00:23:43.599 --> 00:23:44.400
Your Majesty,

00:23:45.000 --> 00:23:46.680
I have a question.

00:23:47.799 --> 00:23:49.079
As far as I know,

00:23:49.960 --> 00:23:52.279
Xuanqing resigned from

00:23:52.559 --> 00:23:54.119
the Hanlin Academy a month ago.

00:23:54.440 --> 00:23:55.599
So why is he

00:23:55.839 --> 00:23:57.160
here today

00:23:57.400 --> 00:24:00.240
in place of Lecturer Liu?

00:24:01.440 --> 00:24:03.279
Who arranged all this?

00:24:03.559 --> 00:24:05.359
How did he enter the palace?

00:24:05.720 --> 00:24:07.000
And what exactly does

00:24:07.440 --> 00:24:09.000
the man behind this want?

00:24:09.680 --> 00:24:11.200
No need to hint

00:24:11.359 --> 00:24:12.519
at a conspiracy.

00:24:13.720 --> 00:24:14.880
I took him

00:24:15.359 --> 00:24:16.599
into the palace.

00:24:21.240 --> 00:24:22.000
Your Majesty,

00:24:22.680 --> 00:24:24.200
several days ago,

00:24:24.559 --> 00:24:26.200
Xuanqing came to me

00:24:26.720 --> 00:24:28.519
and told me all

00:24:28.960 --> 00:24:30.079
his grievances.

00:24:31.359 --> 00:24:32.480
I couldn't bear

00:24:32.480 --> 00:24:34.119
to see such

00:24:34.720 --> 00:24:36.160
talent wasted

00:24:36.160 --> 00:24:37.680
because of Yanyun's

00:24:37.920 --> 00:24:39.359
private grudge.

00:24:39.839 --> 00:24:41.599
So I asked him

00:24:42.279 --> 00:24:44.000
if he dared to confront Yanyun in court.

00:24:44.000 --> 00:24:44.880
He said he did.

00:24:46.160 --> 00:24:46.880
So I

00:24:47.279 --> 00:24:48.079
brought him here

00:24:48.599 --> 00:24:50.240
and gave him a chance to be heard.

00:24:50.599 --> 00:24:53.000
Master, how righteous of you.

00:24:54.079 --> 00:24:55.319
But Your Excellency,

00:24:56.640 --> 00:24:59.599
you've violated court procedure.

00:25:00.079 --> 00:25:01.720
Don't change the subject.

00:25:02.559 --> 00:25:03.559
Remember,

00:25:03.880 --> 00:25:06.480
rules yield to circumstances.

00:25:08.119 --> 00:25:10.799
Well said.

00:25:11.200 --> 00:25:12.119
Xuanqing!

00:25:12.599 --> 00:25:14.319
You're no child

00:25:15.000 --> 00:25:17.200
and should know the consequences.

00:25:24.640 --> 00:25:26.599
Are you threatening him?

00:25:27.000 --> 00:25:27.720
Minister Chen,

00:25:28.119 --> 00:25:29.119
you may defend

00:25:29.279 --> 00:25:30.160
yourself now.

00:25:31.119 --> 00:25:31.680
Your Majesty,

00:25:32.240 --> 00:25:32.799
I

00:25:33.400 --> 00:25:35.559
have a few questions for Xuanqing.

00:25:36.640 --> 00:25:37.200
Go ahead.

00:25:43.799 --> 00:25:44.559
Xuanqing,

00:25:45.279 --> 00:25:47.880
did you come here today to impeach me

00:25:48.400 --> 00:25:49.680
of your own accord

00:25:50.920 --> 00:25:52.400
or were you coerced?

00:25:58.240 --> 00:25:59.000
[Your Excellency!]

00:25:59.680 --> 00:26:01.359
Your Excellency! Your Excellency!

00:26:02.519 --> 00:26:03.680
It's not that I won't obey you,

00:26:04.079 --> 00:26:04.720
but

00:26:06.279 --> 00:26:08.319
to impeach my uncle

00:26:09.920 --> 00:26:11.559
is like denouncing my own dad.

00:26:12.279 --> 00:26:13.119
Even if I succeed,

00:26:13.759 --> 00:26:15.240
my career will be finished.

00:26:17.640 --> 00:26:18.519
I'm sorry.

00:26:19.200 --> 00:26:20.720
I really can't do this.

00:26:20.960 --> 00:26:22.400
You've committed murder.

00:26:22.559 --> 00:26:24.240
What career is there left to protect?

00:26:24.480 --> 00:26:25.200
Besides...

00:26:42.839 --> 00:26:44.759
The third graduate in imperial exams

00:26:45.279 --> 00:26:46.640
and Grand Secretary's nephew

00:26:47.160 --> 00:26:49.440
turns out to be a bandit's son.

00:26:49.759 --> 00:26:51.319
How fascinating.

00:27:02.680 --> 00:27:03.640
I came of my own will.

00:27:04.880 --> 00:27:06.119
No one forced me.

00:27:13.039 --> 00:27:14.160
Is your conscience clear?

00:27:15.559 --> 00:27:17.000
[The bandit's son]

00:27:17.319 --> 00:27:18.519
[took the imperial exams]

00:27:19.640 --> 00:27:21.079
and even ranked third.

00:27:23.240 --> 00:27:24.039
For deceiving the Emperor

00:27:24.039 --> 00:27:25.119
alone,

00:27:27.640 --> 00:27:28.599
you'll

00:27:29.640 --> 00:27:30.759
lose your title at best.

00:27:30.839 --> 00:27:31.680
At worst,

00:27:32.160 --> 00:27:33.519
you'll be imprisoned or exiled.

00:27:39.359 --> 00:27:41.400
As for the murder...

00:27:55.480 --> 00:27:56.079
Yes.

00:27:58.039 --> 00:27:59.920
Everything I've said is the truth.

00:28:02.359 --> 00:28:03.599
You drove me to this.

00:28:07.359 --> 00:28:08.960
You don't regret it?

00:28:11.000 --> 00:28:12.839
[You even played the clown on stage.]

00:28:13.200 --> 00:28:14.680
What is there left to fear?

00:28:15.920 --> 00:28:19.480
Instead of dying unknown,

00:28:20.160 --> 00:28:21.400
why not take a shot

00:28:22.200 --> 00:28:24.480
and make your name

00:28:25.519 --> 00:28:26.799
before the court?

00:28:48.720 --> 00:28:50.319
No.

00:29:04.599 --> 00:29:05.319
Fine.

00:29:08.400 --> 00:29:09.319
Great.

00:29:15.279 --> 00:29:16.000
Your Majesty,

00:29:16.599 --> 00:29:17.240
I

00:29:17.599 --> 00:29:18.359
have no more questions

00:29:19.480 --> 00:29:20.160
and

00:29:21.279 --> 00:29:22.799
nothing to say in my defense.

00:29:24.319 --> 00:29:25.240
Chen Xuanqing

00:29:25.799 --> 00:29:26.759
has turned on me,

00:29:27.279 --> 00:29:28.559
shamed the Chen family,

00:29:28.920 --> 00:29:29.920
spouted nonsense,

00:29:30.160 --> 00:29:31.200
and defied Your Majesty.

00:29:31.680 --> 00:29:32.400
But I must

00:29:32.759 --> 00:29:34.400
still consider my wife and my family.

00:29:37.319 --> 00:29:39.759
As for his accusations against me,

00:29:42.920 --> 00:29:43.960
I'm not someone

00:29:44.160 --> 00:29:46.680
who swears oaths to prove his innocence.

00:29:50.599 --> 00:29:51.400
I can only say

00:29:51.720 --> 00:29:52.880
that truth is plain

00:29:53.319 --> 00:29:54.559
for all to see.

00:30:37.440 --> 00:30:39.160
This is utterly outrageous!

00:30:39.359 --> 00:30:40.119
Court dismissed!

00:30:40.720 --> 00:30:42.400
Minister Chen, come with me.

00:30:42.799 --> 00:30:44.000
I need to know

00:30:44.119 --> 00:30:45.119
what exactly has happened.

00:31:04.039 --> 00:31:04.960
That felt good.

00:31:06.240 --> 00:31:07.079
Really good.

00:31:10.160 --> 00:31:11.160
Today, before His Majesty

00:31:11.680 --> 00:31:13.359
and the entire court,

00:31:13.839 --> 00:31:15.160
I exposed you

00:31:15.160 --> 00:31:16.799
for the hypocrite

00:31:17.759 --> 00:31:18.559
you are,

00:31:18.559 --> 00:31:20.119
Chen Yanyun.

00:31:20.920 --> 00:31:21.880
What do I have to fear?

00:31:23.160 --> 00:31:24.400
What is there to fear?

00:31:26.720 --> 00:31:27.680
Even His Excellency's

00:31:27.680 --> 00:31:28.920
no my side.

00:31:29.279 --> 00:31:29.920
I have

00:31:29.920 --> 00:31:31.200
nothing to fear.

00:31:36.079 --> 00:31:36.960
Chen Yanyun,

00:31:38.559 --> 00:31:40.279
you can only blame yourself.

00:31:40.880 --> 00:31:42.279
You're shameless

00:31:42.559 --> 00:31:43.839
and pushed me too far.

00:31:48.359 --> 00:31:49.160
Now with

00:31:49.160 --> 00:31:50.519
His Excellency's help,

00:31:51.359 --> 00:31:53.039
my rise is assured.

00:31:54.799 --> 00:31:55.559
But you?

00:31:56.680 --> 00:31:57.599
Chen Yanyun,

00:31:58.240 --> 00:31:59.599
your reputation ruined,

00:31:59.920 --> 00:32:01.359
your career destroyed.

00:32:02.799 --> 00:32:04.480
You'll be at my mercy.

00:32:14.160 --> 00:32:14.839
Who is it?

00:32:15.519 --> 00:32:17.640
Lord Chen, it's time to go now.

00:32:52.319 --> 00:32:54.519
Of course he couldn't defend himself.

00:32:56.519 --> 00:32:58.000
Grand Secretary accused by

00:32:58.839 --> 00:33:02.200
his nephew of taking his bride-to-be.

00:33:04.799 --> 00:33:06.759
Whether it's true or not,

00:33:06.880 --> 00:33:08.200
once this spreads,

00:33:09.240 --> 00:33:12.039
it becomes a scandal that disgraces

00:33:12.359 --> 00:33:15.160
His Majesty and the court.

00:33:16.839 --> 00:33:19.440
Even if His Majesty wanted to protect him,

00:33:20.759 --> 00:33:22.279
there is nothing he can do.

00:33:23.519 --> 00:33:24.720
Exactly.

00:33:27.000 --> 00:33:29.960
Poor Gu Jinzhao.

00:33:32.559 --> 00:33:33.799
Such a clever girl.

00:33:34.240 --> 00:33:36.000
Yet of all men,

00:33:37.160 --> 00:33:38.279
she chose Yanyun.

00:33:44.039 --> 00:33:44.599
Ma'am,

00:33:45.000 --> 00:33:46.119
Ms. Qinglan is here.

00:33:46.839 --> 00:33:47.759
Qinglan?

00:33:49.200 --> 00:33:50.079
Lately,

00:33:50.079 --> 00:33:52.039
she's been investigating cases with Ye Xian.

00:33:53.400 --> 00:33:54.480
Now she

00:33:55.319 --> 00:33:56.920
finally remembers to visit me.

00:33:58.240 --> 00:33:59.960
[Chen Xuanqing has sided with His Excellency]

00:34:00.079 --> 00:34:01.160
- [to bring Mr. Chen down.]
- Hyah!

00:34:01.440 --> 00:34:02.839
[If His Excellency finds out]

00:34:03.079 --> 00:34:04.480
- [the Criminal Investigation Bureau files]
- Hyah!

00:34:04.480 --> 00:34:05.440
[in the Ji family,]
[we'll be in serious trouble.]

00:34:06.519 --> 00:34:06.920
Hyah!

00:34:12.119 --> 00:34:13.360
How

00:34:14.800 --> 00:34:16.000
did you know this?

00:34:16.880 --> 00:34:18.280
Xian was ordered to root out

00:34:18.280 --> 00:34:19.719
the Chunyuan remnants in Xuanfu.

00:34:19.960 --> 00:34:20.960
I went with him.

00:34:21.440 --> 00:34:23.000
Later, we split up.

00:34:23.960 --> 00:34:24.880
I did

00:34:25.320 --> 00:34:26.159
manage to

00:34:26.159 --> 00:34:27.960
capture a few of them.

00:34:28.400 --> 00:34:29.840
One of them claimed that

00:34:30.199 --> 00:34:32.159
even before Prince Chengqing's rebellion,

00:34:32.400 --> 00:34:34.000
he personally saw you and Uncle Fu

00:34:34.000 --> 00:34:35.760
at one of their gatherings.

00:34:39.000 --> 00:34:40.039
That's impossible.

00:34:40.800 --> 00:34:42.159
They must be lying.

00:34:43.719 --> 00:34:44.639
But he gave
many details.

00:34:45.719 --> 00:34:46.760
It's hard to tell.

00:34:47.480 --> 00:34:48.880
Of course it's false.

00:34:52.719 --> 00:34:53.800
What do you plan to do?

00:34:54.320 --> 00:34:55.679
Nothing, of course.

00:34:57.000 --> 00:34:58.519
I've taken care of that guy.

00:34:58.679 --> 00:35:00.719
I can't just let them slander you.

00:35:03.239 --> 00:35:04.360
Does Ye Xian...

00:35:04.719 --> 00:35:05.480
He doesn't know.

00:35:10.480 --> 00:35:11.480
Qinglan,

00:35:12.280 --> 00:35:13.440
good job.

00:35:14.320 --> 00:35:15.400
I've always

00:35:15.920 --> 00:35:16.679
treated you

00:35:16.679 --> 00:35:18.320
like my own daughter.

00:35:19.079 --> 00:35:20.400
His words were

00:35:20.800 --> 00:35:21.679
clearly slander,

00:35:22.280 --> 00:35:23.039
but

00:35:23.599 --> 00:35:24.760
the fewer people know,

00:35:25.000 --> 00:35:26.159
the better.

00:35:27.239 --> 00:35:27.960
Exactly.

00:35:29.800 --> 00:35:30.840
But he

00:35:30.840 --> 00:35:32.800
even dare frame you.

00:35:32.880 --> 00:35:34.199
This is outrageous.

00:35:34.719 --> 00:35:36.599
There's definitely someone behind him.

00:35:36.880 --> 00:35:37.639
He may even be

00:35:37.639 --> 00:35:39.400
of the Chunyuan Sect's inner circle.

00:35:41.119 --> 00:35:42.119
Don't worry.

00:35:42.920 --> 00:35:44.639
I've sent people to look into it quietly.

00:35:45.039 --> 00:35:46.119
Following the trail,

00:35:46.559 --> 00:35:47.960
we'll surely find out

00:35:48.199 --> 00:35:49.280
who is behind this.

00:35:55.880 --> 00:35:57.039
It's fine for you to investigate,

00:35:57.840 --> 00:35:58.679
but

00:35:59.039 --> 00:36:00.400
do it quietly.

00:36:01.119 --> 00:36:02.239
This involves

00:36:02.480 --> 00:36:03.960
the Chunyuan remnants.

00:36:04.159 --> 00:36:05.159
If word gets out,

00:36:05.440 --> 00:36:07.760
your uncle will be implicated.

00:36:09.800 --> 00:36:11.639
Come to me the moment

00:36:11.880 --> 00:36:13.480
you find anything.

00:36:14.840 --> 00:36:15.840
You're right.

00:36:16.239 --> 00:36:17.280
I'll be careful.

00:36:22.280 --> 00:36:24.039
Get out! Both of you!

00:36:29.360 --> 00:36:30.039
Minister Chen,

00:36:30.480 --> 00:36:31.599
I wasn't confused.

00:36:32.360 --> 00:36:32.840
No.

00:36:33.559 --> 00:36:34.639
Perhaps I was.

00:36:35.039 --> 00:36:36.000
I thought

00:36:36.000 --> 00:36:37.079
Chen Xuanqing's your nephew,

00:36:37.519 --> 00:36:38.079
so I gave him
a chance to prove himself.

00:36:39.280 --> 00:36:40.079
Who would have expected

00:36:40.159 --> 00:36:41.400
that bastard to defy the throne

00:36:41.400 --> 00:36:42.199
and betray you?

00:36:43.679 --> 00:36:45.199
I'm really sorry.

00:36:47.239 --> 00:36:48.159
Your Majesty, please

00:36:48.239 --> 00:36:49.800
don't say that.

00:36:50.119 --> 00:36:51.880
I fail to manage the household well.

00:36:53.960 --> 00:36:54.639
Though

00:36:55.039 --> 00:36:56.280
I did not expect Master

00:36:56.519 --> 00:36:58.239
to turn Xuanqing against me,

00:36:59.360 --> 00:37:00.199
fortunately,

00:37:01.199 --> 00:37:03.239
it didn't stray far from my plan.

00:37:04.440 --> 00:37:05.039
Right.

00:37:06.079 --> 00:37:06.880
With

00:37:07.320 --> 00:37:08.559
or without Chen Xuanqing

00:37:08.920 --> 00:37:09.920
and Wang Xuanfan,

00:37:10.079 --> 00:37:11.920
Mr. Fu would've suppressed you anyway,

00:37:12.079 --> 00:37:13.920
to control the entire court.

00:37:14.320 --> 00:37:15.559
So cutting frontier troops

00:37:15.559 --> 00:37:16.480
and slashing military spending

00:37:16.639 --> 00:37:17.760
can be decided by him alone.

00:37:18.360 --> 00:37:20.000
You foresaw all of this.

00:37:20.639 --> 00:37:21.360
Tell me,
if he's

00:37:22.280 --> 00:37:23.440
colluding with Northern Barbarians,

00:37:24.239 --> 00:37:25.280
would he commit treason?

00:37:26.199 --> 00:37:27.000
What if...

00:37:27.360 --> 00:37:28.800
What if they invade us?

00:37:29.280 --> 00:37:30.320
That is unlikely.

00:37:30.760 --> 00:37:31.840
How can you be sure?

00:37:33.000 --> 00:37:33.639
Your Majesty,

00:37:34.880 --> 00:37:36.599
these are only suspicions.

00:37:37.079 --> 00:37:37.639
At present,
there are

00:37:38.599 --> 00:37:39.800
only two urgent matters.

00:37:40.440 --> 00:37:42.840
Crack down all the active

00:37:43.000 --> 00:37:44.480
Chunyuan remnants in Great Yan.

00:37:44.880 --> 00:37:45.599
That's one thing.

00:37:46.679 --> 00:37:48.480
Quietly win over the military nobles,

00:37:48.679 --> 00:37:49.519
in case the worst should come.

00:37:50.079 --> 00:37:50.880
That's the other.

00:37:52.639 --> 00:37:53.320
But

00:37:53.519 --> 00:37:54.599
both must be

00:37:55.360 --> 00:37:56.760
kept from Fu.

00:37:57.440 --> 00:37:58.000
Okay.

00:37:58.880 --> 00:37:59.679
I will

00:37:59.960 --> 00:38:00.480
write to

00:38:00.480 --> 00:38:01.679
Lord Jingyuan and the others.

00:38:12.039 --> 00:38:12.760
Your Majesty,

00:38:13.480 --> 00:38:14.639
take it easy.

00:38:15.159 --> 00:38:16.400
We can still turn the tables.

00:38:17.320 --> 00:38:18.159
Now that

00:38:18.679 --> 00:38:20.360
I bear this charge,

00:38:20.639 --> 00:38:21.760
Fu may

00:38:22.239 --> 00:38:23.320
lower his guard.

00:38:24.440 --> 00:38:25.199
It'll be easier

00:38:26.000 --> 00:38:27.119
for me to make moves.

00:38:27.719 --> 00:38:28.360
So just

00:38:28.599 --> 00:38:30.360
handle whatever comes your way.

00:38:30.599 --> 00:38:31.559
Leave

00:38:32.360 --> 00:38:33.199
the rest to me.

00:38:34.239 --> 00:38:34.679
Good.

00:38:35.519 --> 00:38:36.480
With you here,

00:38:36.840 --> 00:38:37.880
I have nothing to worry about.

00:38:42.679 --> 00:38:43.440
Thanks, Your Majesty.
I'll take

00:38:45.559 --> 00:38:46.119
my leave.

00:39:17.580 --> 00:39:18.080
Sir.

00:39:45.719 --> 00:39:46.360
Sir,

00:39:47.440 --> 00:39:48.519
everyone from the Ji family

00:39:48.679 --> 00:39:49.599
is here.

00:40:02.159 --> 00:40:03.239
Let them go,

00:40:03.679 --> 00:40:04.719
or I'll kill you.

00:40:10.519 --> 00:40:12.000
You think I'm afraid of death?

00:40:12.920 --> 00:40:14.320
You're insane.

00:40:14.639 --> 00:40:15.079
Yes,

00:40:16.239 --> 00:40:17.400
I am.

00:40:19.239 --> 00:40:21.079
To make Chen Yanyun,

00:40:21.400 --> 00:40:22.840
the lofty Chancellor,

00:40:22.840 --> 00:40:24.239
bow his head and beg me on his knees,

00:40:24.719 --> 00:40:25.840
I'll do whatever it takes,

00:40:26.360 --> 00:40:27.519
even if it costs me my life.

00:40:32.280 --> 00:40:33.400
He should be here soon.

00:40:35.760 --> 00:40:37.119
Take them all back to the Court of Judicial.

00:40:40.559 --> 00:40:41.599
Jinzhao!

00:40:44.280 --> 00:40:45.480
When Chen Yanyun arrives,

00:40:46.960 --> 00:40:48.400
tell him to kneel and beg me.

00:40:52.480 --> 00:40:53.440
Perhaps then,

00:40:53.840 --> 00:40:55.360
I'll spare the Ji family.

00:40:57.360 --> 00:40:58.400
Keep dreaming.

00:41:17.639 --> 00:41:18.440
Yanyun?

00:41:26.239 --> 00:41:26.719
Sir,

00:41:27.000 --> 00:41:28.280
I was only following orders.

00:41:35.960 --> 00:41:36.760
Yanyun.

00:41:37.599 --> 00:41:39.199
You ungrateful bastard!

00:41:44.280 --> 00:41:45.360
Go save Grandma.

00:41:46.719 --> 00:41:47.320
Are you alright?

00:41:48.079 --> 00:41:48.880
It's only a shallow cut.

00:41:54.599 --> 00:41:56.199
Jinzhao, are you okay?

00:41:56.199 --> 00:41:56.800
I'm fine.

00:41:59.840 --> 00:42:00.880
Xuanqing,

00:42:01.119 --> 00:42:03.239
I never thought you'd do such things.

00:42:03.280 --> 00:42:04.840
You're a monster.

00:42:09.199 --> 00:42:09.960
Yanyun,

00:42:10.920 --> 00:42:12.199
I know what you've hidden

00:42:12.199 --> 00:42:13.239
in the Ji family.

00:42:14.480 --> 00:42:15.400
Once my men

00:42:16.000 --> 00:42:17.360
find them,

00:42:18.280 --> 00:42:19.519
you'll all be doomed.

00:42:22.280 --> 00:42:23.079
Is that so?

00:42:24.400 --> 00:42:24.880
Yeah,

00:42:26.800 --> 00:42:27.480
unless

00:42:29.960 --> 00:42:31.320
you beg me on your knees.

00:42:34.039 --> 00:42:34.880
Beg you

00:42:35.360 --> 00:42:36.119
on my knees?

00:42:38.400 --> 00:42:38.920
Exactly.

00:42:40.400 --> 00:42:41.280
Yanyun,

00:42:41.840 --> 00:42:43.679
look how far you've fallen.

00:42:51.320 --> 00:42:52.199
Idiot.

00:42:52.679 --> 00:42:53.320
You know why

00:42:53.320 --> 00:42:54.559
I sent you out of the capital.

00:42:55.440 --> 00:42:56.559
You know nothing

00:42:57.679 --> 00:42:59.079
of how the court works.

00:43:02.559 --> 00:43:03.119
Let go!

00:43:05.440 --> 00:43:05.920
Let go!
Let go of me!

00:43:07.119 --> 00:43:07.760
Let me go!
Let...

00:43:18.480 --> 00:43:19.239
What are you doing?